Router_MAIN

enable
configure terminal
interface Serial 0/3/0
no shutdown
ip address 99.99.90.1 255.255.255.0
interface Serial 0/3/1
no shutdown
ip address 99.99.91.1 255.255.255.0
interface Serial 0/2/0
no shutdown
ip address 99.99.92.1 255.255.255.0
exit

ip route 10.1.0.0 255.255.0.0 99.99.90.2
ip route 10.2.0.0 255.255.0.0 99.99.91.2
ip route 10.3.0.0 255.255.0.0 99.99.91.2
ip route 10.10.0.0 255.255.0.0 99.99.91.2